As of 4:00 PM SAST on Thursday, May 29, 2025, the weather in Cape Town is partly sunny with a temperature of 66°F (19°C).

## Weather for Cape Town, South Africa:
Current Conditions: Partly sunny, 66°F (19°C)

Daily Forecast:
* Thursday, May 29: Low: 54°F (12°C), High: 64°F (18°C), Description: Intervals of clouds and sunshine; breezy this afternoon
* Friday, May 30: Low: 55°F (13°C), High: 64°F (18°C), Description: A shower in spots in the morning; otherwise, sunny much of the time
* Saturday, May 31: Low: 50°F (10°C), High: 64°F (18°C), Description: Partly sunny
* Sunday, June 1: Low: 51°F (11°C), High: 64°F (18°C), Description: Sun and areas of low clouds
* Monday, June 2: Low: 54°F (12°C), High: 65°F (18°C), Description: After a cloudy start, sun returns
* Tuesday, June 3: Low: 50°F (10°C), High: 61°F (16°C), Description: Occasional rain in the morning; otherwise, cloudy
* Wednesday, June 4: Low: 46°F (8°C), High: 63°F (17°C), Description: Plenty of sunshine
